					<description><![CDATA[<p><img width="1280" height="1280" src="https://firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/samoyed-2400687_1280.jpg" class="attachment-post-thumbnail size-post-thumbnail wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" srcset="https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/samoyed-2400687_1280.jpg?w=1280&amp;ssl=1 1280w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/samoyed-2400687_1280.jpg?resize=150%2C150&amp;ssl=1 150w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/samoyed-2400687_1280.jpg?resize=768%2C768&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/samoyed-2400687_1280.jpg?resize=146%2C146&amp;ssl=1 146w" sizes="(max-width: 1280px) 100vw, 1280px" /></p>
<p>火報記者 洪瑜蓉 / 綜合報導&#160; 你有看過這麼軟萌無辜的狗狗嗎？近日國外一名飼主分享自家薩摩耶犬的無 &#8230;</p>
<p>這篇文章 <a href="https://firenews.com.tw/2025/07/16/%e5%81%9a%e9%8c%af%e4%ba%8b%e4%b9%9f%e7%bd%b5%e4%b8%8d%e5%be%97%ef%bc%9f%e8%b6%85%e8%90%8c%e8%96%a9%e6%91%a9%e8%80%b6%e4%b8%80%e8%87%89%e7%84%a1%e8%be%9c%e6%93%84%e7%8d%b2%e7%b6%b2%e5%8f%8b%e5%80%91/">做錯事也罵不得？超萌薩摩耶一臉無辜擄獲網友們芳心 </a> 最早出現於 <a href="https://firenews.com.tw">火報</a>。</p>
]]></description>
										<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><img width="1280" height="1280" src="https://firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/samoyed-2400687_1280.jpg" class="attachment-post-thumbnail size-post-thumbnail wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" srcset="https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/samoyed-2400687_1280.jpg?w=1280&amp;ssl=1 1280w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/samoyed-2400687_1280.jpg?resize=150%2C150&amp;ssl=1 150w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/samoyed-2400687_1280.jpg?resize=768%2C768&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/samoyed-2400687_1280.jpg?resize=146%2C146&amp;ssl=1 146w" sizes="(max-width: 1280px) 100vw, 1280px" /></p>
<p>火報記者 洪瑜蓉 / 綜合報導&nbsp;</p>



<p>你有看過這麼軟萌無辜的狗狗嗎？近日國外一名飼主分享自家薩摩耶犬的無俚頭反應，引起網友熱烈討論，這隻毛茸茸的大白狗，只要一被罵或者感覺自己受了委屈，就會立刻癱倒在地，表情出生無可戀的模樣，總是讓主人哭笑不得。&nbsp;</p>



<p>該名飼主表示，自家養的這隻薩摩耶犬從小就有著跟其他狗狗不同的性格，平時裡雖然能帶給大家歡笑，但只要每當牠稍微闖禍而被責備時，整隻狗就會瞬間癱軟，無力地躺在床上或者沙發上，仿佛像棉花糖一般完全沒了骨頭。&nbsp;</p>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-full"><img decoding="async" width="1220" height="593" src="https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/samoyed-3998156_1280.jpg?resize=1220%2C593&#038;ssl=1" alt="" class="wp-image-227568" srcset="https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/samoyed-3998156_1280.jpg?w=1280&amp;ssl=1 1280w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/samoyed-3998156_1280.jpg?resize=768%2C373&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/samoyed-3998156_1280.jpg?resize=260%2C126&amp;ssl=1 260w" sizes="(max-width: 1220px) 100vw, 1220px" data-recalc-dims="1" /><figcaption class="wp-element-caption">狗狗每次只要闖禍被責罵，就會瞬間癱軟倒在床上，表現出生無可戀的模樣<br>(示意圖/Pixabay)</figcaption></figure>



<p>更有趣的是，只要當狗狗進入這種狀況，那麼無論主人如何安撫愛犬的情緒，牠都會堅持不動，像是在透過身體語言來表達自己的委屈，這番反應也讓飼主感到又好氣又好笑，完全拿自家的狗狗無可奈何，絲毫沒有半點方法。&nbsp;</p>



<p>薩摩耶搞笑又惹人心疼的反應曝光後，迅速引起網上熱議，許多網友紛紛留言調侃「太會演了」、「受不得半點委屈」、「可以參加奧斯卡」、「一被罵就開大絕招」、「好可愛，不像我家的狗狗只會裝聽不見」、「戲精一枚」、「根本免死金牌」。&nbsp;</p>
<p>這篇文章 <a href="https://firenews.com.tw/2025/07/16/%e5%81%9a%e9%8c%af%e4%ba%8b%e4%b9%9f%e7%bd%b5%e4%b8%8d%e5%be%97%ef%bc%9f%e8%b6%85%e8%90%8c%e8%96%a9%e6%91%a9%e8%80%b6%e4%b8%80%e8%87%89%e7%84%a1%e8%be%9c%e6%93%84%e7%8d%b2%e7%b6%b2%e5%8f%8b%e5%80%91/">做錯事也罵不得？超萌薩摩耶一臉無辜擄獲網友們芳心 </a> 最早出現於 <a href="https://firenews.com.tw">火報</a>。</p>
]]></content:encoded>
					
		
		
