<p>火報記者 洪瑜蓉 / 綜合報導&#160; 最近有名飼主分享自家柴犬在日常的散步途中，竟意外發生了一場跨越種族 &#8230;</p>
<p>這篇文章 <a href="https://firenews.com.tw/2025/07/16/%e6%95%a3%e6%ad%a5%e7%aa%81%e7%84%b6%e8%ae%8a%e4%b8%89%e5%af%b6%e5%aa%bd%ef%bc%9f%e5%b0%8f%e8%b2%93%e7%b7%8a%e8%b7%9f%e6%9f%b4%e7%8a%ac%e5%9b%9e%e5%ae%b6%e8%ae%93%e9%a3%bc%e4%b8%bb%e8%b6%85%e5%82%bb/">散步突然變三寶媽？小貓緊跟柴犬回家讓飼主超傻眼 </a> 最早出現於 <a href="https://firenews.com.tw">火報</a>。</p>
]]></description>
										<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><img width="2560" height="1707" src="https://firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/michael-myers-dw2gsogcW00-unsplash-scaled.jpg" class="attachment-post-thumbnail size-post-thumbnail wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" srcset="https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/michael-myers-dw2gsogcW00-unsplash-scaled.jpg?w=2560&amp;ssl=1 2560w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/michael-myers-dw2gsogcW00-unsplash-scaled.jpg?resize=768%2C512&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/michael-myers-dw2gsogcW00-unsplash-scaled.jpg?resize=1536%2C1024&amp;ssl=1 1536w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/michael-myers-dw2gsogcW00-unsplash-scaled.jpg?resize=2048%2C1365&amp;ssl=1 2048w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/michael-myers-dw2gsogcW00-unsplash-scaled.jpg?resize=219%2C146&amp;ssl=1 219w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/michael-myers-dw2gsogcW00-unsplash-scaled.jpg?w=2440&amp;ssl=1 2440w" sizes="(max-width: 2560px) 100vw, 2560px" /></p>
<p>火報記者 洪瑜蓉 / 綜合報導&nbsp;</p>



<p>最近有名飼主分享自家柴犬在日常的散步途中，竟意外發生了一場跨越種族的認親事件，愛犬在回家路上遭到三隻流浪小奶貓一路緊緊相隨，小貓仿佛將狗狗誤認成自己的媽媽，場面溫馨又令人感到驚訝。&nbsp;</p>



<p>據了解，當時這隻溫馴的柴犬只是如往常一樣外出散步，卻在途中巧遇了三隻孤伶伶的小奶貓，小貓們看起來年紀尚幼，疑似不慎與貓媽媽走失，並將柴犬誤認為自己的母親，於是一路緊跟在狗狗身後，甚至還試圖向牠討奶喝。&nbsp;</p>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-full"><img decoding="async" width="1220" height="813" src="https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/road-ahead-gGU3lanpKAs-unsplash-scaled.jpg?resize=1220%2C813&#038;ssl=1" alt="" class="wp-image-227572" srcset="https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/road-ahead-gGU3lanpKAs-unsplash-scaled.jpg?w=2560&amp;ssl=1 2560w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/road-ahead-gGU3lanpKAs-unsplash-scaled.jpg?resize=768%2C512&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/road-ahead-gGU3lanpKAs-unsplash-scaled.jpg?resize=1536%2C1024&amp;ssl=1 1536w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/road-ahead-gGU3lanpKAs-unsplash-scaled.jpg?resize=2048%2C1365&amp;ssl=1 2048w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/road-ahead-gGU3lanpKAs-unsplash-scaled.jpg?resize=219%2C146&amp;ssl=1 219w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/road-ahead-gGU3lanpKAs-unsplash-scaled.jpg?w=2440&amp;ssl=1 2440w" sizes="(max-width: 1220px) 100vw, 1220px" data-recalc-dims="1" /><figcaption class="wp-element-caption">流浪小奶媽將狗狗誤認為自己的母親，最終成功被飼主收編<br>(示意圖/Unsplash) </figcaption></figure>



<p>讓人意外的是，對此柴犬並無感到排斥，反而還不時回頭查看小貓是否有掉隊，一路帶著小奶貓們回到飼主身邊，露出楚楚可憐的表情看著主人，像是在懇求飼主收編牠們一樣。&nbsp;</p>



<p>面對自家愛犬突如其來變成三寶媽的窘境，飼主當場楞在原地不知道該如何是好，但最終在狗狗渴望的眼神攻勢之下，飼主還是決定將三隻奶貓一同收留，事件曝光引起網友熱議，不少人笑稱「也太奇葩」、「搞不好真的是狗狗生的」、「母愛不分物種」。&nbsp;</p>
<p>這篇文章 <a href="https://firenews.com.tw/2025/07/16/%e6%95%a3%e6%ad%a5%e7%aa%81%e7%84%b6%e8%ae%8a%e4%b8%89%e5%af%b6%e5%aa%bd%ef%bc%9f%e5%b0%8f%e8%b2%93%e7%b7%8a%e8%b7%9f%e6%9f%b4%e7%8a%ac%e5%9b%9e%e5%ae%b6%e8%ae%93%e9%a3%bc%e4%b8%bb%e8%b6%85%e5%82%bb/">散步突然變三寶媽？小貓緊跟柴犬回家讓飼主超傻眼 </a> 最早出現於 <a href="https://firenews.com.tw">火報</a>。</p>
]]></content:encoded>
					
		
		
