					<description><![CDATA[<p><img width="500" height="333" src="https://firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/image-167.png" class="attachment-post-thumbnail size-post-thumbnail wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" srcset="https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/image-167.png?w=500&amp;ssl=1 500w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/image-167.png?resize=219%2C146&amp;ssl=1 219w" sizes="(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px" /></p>
